data.description: ASK ME HOW TO OWN THIS HOME WITH  ABSOLUTELY NO DOWN PAYMENT, $5,000 GRANT FOR CLOSING COST & NO PMI.  This contemporary townhouse, located at 5427 White Mane, offers a perfect blend of comfort and convenience. The main level features an eat-in kitchen, and the adjacent dining area is ideal for intimate gatherings or enjoying family meals. Make your way upstairs to discover three generously sized bedrooms. The primary bedroom boasts a private bathroom, offering a tranquil oasis after a long day. With one assigned parking space along with additional unassigned spaces; parking will never be a hassle. The community amenities include a walking path and playground, perfect for children to enjoy outdoor activities and make new friends. This prime location offers easy access to The Mall in Columbia, Symphony Woods park, and the Howard County Parks systems, providing endless opportunities for shopping, dining, and outdoor recreation. Well maintained with the following updates:  new carpet, fresh paint, new roof (2022), new furnace (2023), hot water heater (2010), washer (2015), gutter guards (2017), windows replaced. Seller will include home warranty which expires August 2024. Don't miss the chance to make this exceptional property your own. Schedule a showing today and experience the epitome of comfortable living in Columbia, Maryland!
